- **Transaction Queue**: Shows pending transactions and active customers
- **Notification System**: Bell icon with badge count, dismissible notification panel
- **Live Clock**: Current time display with system status timestamp
- **Auto-refresh**: 30-second interval health checks with status change notifications

#### **2. Payment Status Monitor** (`components/pos/payment/PaymentStatusMonitor.tsx`)
- **Real-time Payment Tracking**: Live progress bars and status updates
- **Method-Specific Flows**: Different processing stages for Lightning, Bitcoin, USDT
- **Visual Feedback**: Icons, progress bars, and status badges
- **Countdown Timer**: Payment expiration tracking with real-time updates
- **Transaction Details**: Payment ID, confirmation counts, transaction hashes
- **Error Handling**: Retry functionality and detailed error messages
- **Automatic Completion**: Integration with payment modal completion flow

#### **3. Transaction Validator** (`components/pos/TransactionValidator.tsx`)
- **Real-time Validation**: Instant feedback on cart items, pricing, inventory
- **Multi-level Alerts**: Errors (blocking), warnings (informational), info (status)
- **Inventory Checks**: Out-of-stock detection, low stock warnings, quantity validation
